description:
It’s non-stop laughs this week on Unqualified as hilarious comedian, Jay Pharoah (Saturday Night Live) joins Anna and Sim to explore…

  • Working retail and funky feet
  • Porn preferences and thigh-high stockings
  • Year-round Christmas decorations
  • Peeing sitting down and genitalia
  • Beverly Hills Cop improv with Karen Sarducci

On the phones this week…

  • Francisca, 27, is calling from Switzerland seeking advice on whether she should make a big, life-changing move in order to follow her dreams.
  • Allison, 29, calling from Ohio, is struggling to find a balance between her role as a Mom and her role as a wife and seeking advice on how to rekindle her sex life.

Check out Jay Pharoah’s new series Champagne Ill, exclusively on YouTube Premiere!
